      p I teach Kenpo, a system rooted in long-standing tradition with a lineage tracing back over a thousand years to the Shaolin Temple in China, passed down through generations of dedicated martial artists. Lineage and structure matter. They show that the system has been tested, refined, and preserved with purpose.
